Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.18,0:00:04.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,東漢末年 在曹操的猛攻下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.77,0:00:06.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,劉備被迫從新野南下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.22,0:00:11.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,此次逃亡 劉備帶著眾多敬仰他的民眾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.88,0:00:14.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,由於人數過多 行軍速度緩慢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.72,0:00:19.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,被曹操派出的軍隊追上只是時間問題
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.01,0:00:21.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為了加快行軍速度
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.72,0:00:25.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,屬下諫言捨棄民眾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.15,0:00:27.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,卻遭到劉備嚴詞拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.93,0:00:31.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,夫濟大事 必以人為本
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.19,0:00:35.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,仁者劉備 無時無刻不心繫蒼生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.67,0:00:37.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,而在現代
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.99,0:00:40.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,也有一位心繫蒼生的歌手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.39,0:00:43.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為什麼而唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.52,0:00:45.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,必須表現出來才行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.70,0:00:48.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為世界級DJ Kid的一番話煩惱不已的英子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.00,0:00:51.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,與在戶外演出時邂逅的街頭歌手七海
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.78,0:00:53.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,結下了深厚的情誼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.62,0:00:54.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,然而
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.67,0:00:55.93,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,請看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.53,0:00:59.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我是偶像樂隊AZALEA的貝斯手兼主唱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.49,0:01:01.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,久遠七海
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.06,0:01:06.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,原來七海也參加了10萬讚企劃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.23,0:01:08.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是英子的對手 AZALEA的成員
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.45,0:01:10.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,服裝 歌曲 編舞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.56,0:01:12.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,全部要聽從我們的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.81,0:01:17.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,唐澤製作人的方針令七海煩惱不已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.53,0:01:20.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我不想唱唐澤的歌了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.43,0:01:25.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但AZALEA早就不只屬於我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.54,0:01:28.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,英子為了受到傷害的七海
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.67,0:01:31.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為了七海那樣的人 為了蒼生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.03,0:01:33.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我要唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.16,0:01:38.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這意味著英子步入了全新的階段
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.31,0:01:50.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,CHANCE×CHANCE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.14,0:01:51.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,逢！！Chitty Chitty Bang Bang
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.98,0:01:53.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,哀！？Chitty Chitty CHANCE CHANCE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.86,0:01:55.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,嗚呼！Chitty Chitty Bang Bang
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.76,0:01:57.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,愛！！Choki Choki Bang Bang
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.59,0:01:59.43,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,HIGH Chitty Chitty Bang Bang
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.43,0:02:01.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,哀！？Chitty Chitty CHANCE CHANCE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.29,0:02:03.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,嗚呼！Chitty Chitty Bang Bang
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.18,0:02:03.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,愛！！Choki Choki Bang Bang
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.98,0:02:07.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,無論張三李四
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.12,0:02:11.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,全都心血來潮 好難受
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.37,0:02:14.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,龍舌蘭喝到醉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.91,0:02:18.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不存在的妄想連連 閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.63,0:02:23.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,夢是潘多拉 讓人想要打開
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.11,0:02:26.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,大家都期待著派對咖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.18,0:02:30.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,今晚不知道 爬不爬富士山
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.59,0:02:33.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,決戰是週末的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.34,0:02:35.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,CHANCE×CHANCE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.12,0:02:37.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,逢！！Chitty Chitty Bang Bang
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.37,0:02:41.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,別裝模作樣 好好享受 今晚嗨起來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.81,0:02:42.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,CHANCE×CHANCE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.56,0:02:44.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,哀！？Chitty Chitty Bang Bang
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.87,0:02:49.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,無論再鬱悶 今晚也要一起派對
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.37,0:02:50.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,CHANCE×CHANCE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.12,0:02:52.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,嗚呼！Chitty Chitty Bang Bang
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.43,0:02:56.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,愚蠢的人更該HIGH 完美社會
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.81,0:02:57.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,CHANCE×CHANCE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.59,0:02:59.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,愛！！Choki Choki Bang Bang
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.87,0:03:04.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,大家都是明日的超級明星 今晚一起派對
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.06,0:03:15.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（夢想家）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.97,0:03:18.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（距離X日還剩6天）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.37,0:03:32.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我要跟七海對決啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.69,0:03:37.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那卡車最近出現頻率很高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.03,0:03:39.43,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是AZALEA吧 挺棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.93,0:03:44.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,下次見面可能就是敵人了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.66,0:03:45.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.53,0:03:51.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,久遠 我說過吧 必須聽從我的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.40,0:03:52.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,七海不是聽了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.99,0:03:55.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,一夏 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.88,0:03:56.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,七海
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.59,0:03:58.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.12,0:04:00.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你養成了不好的習慣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.43,0:04:05.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你當前的任務是完美練好這首歌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.22,0:04:08.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,而不是上街演唱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.12,0:04:10.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.52,0:04:12.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,別浪費時間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.59,0:04:13.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,再來一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.18,0:04:14.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.94,0:04:22.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,英子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.93,0:04:24.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,KABE 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.10,0:04:26.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,上次真是太感謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.49,0:04:27.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你指什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.74,0:04:31.43,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我嘗試了一下你說的 是回歸原點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.16,0:04:33.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,原點…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.99,0:04:36.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,啊 你還真試了啊 結果怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.72,0:04:38.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我找老家的朋友玩了玩接力說唱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.68,0:04:40.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,感覺有點收穫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.98,0:04:42.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這樣就能跟赤兔馬對決了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.92,0:04:44.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎樣的收穫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.95,0:04:48.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼說呢 就是明白自己是誰了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.61,0:04:50.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,或者說可以隨心所欲地說唱了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.29,0:04:53.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你就等著瞧吧 我會讓他見識到我的厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.11,0:04:55.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.44,0:04:56.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你怎樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.86,0:04:57.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.29,0:05:00.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（布丁老頭）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.70,0:05:01.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.76,0:05:04.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,喂 我是英子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.54,0:05:07.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是時候來個了斷了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.05,0:05:10.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.05,0:05:13.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:14.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,現在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.52,0:05:17.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,嗯 我也得讓他見識見識我的厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.35,0:05:18.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,英子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.89,0:05:21.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,祝你旗開得勝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.69,0:05:25.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.37,0:05:28.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,孔明 你什麼時候來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.00,0:05:34.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,KABE 你跟赤兔馬功夫的對決也快到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.00,0:05:36.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你想給我增加壓力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.86,0:05:40.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒 我只是很確信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.25,0:05:41.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你也能贏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.92,0:05:42.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好沉重
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.45,0:05:45.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那我也得去最後衝刺了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.56,0:05:46.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,祝你旗開得勝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.73,0:05:52.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,兩個想攀上高峰的年輕人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.74,0:05:55.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.70,0:05:57.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,咦？他們人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.51,0:05:59.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,老闆 儘管放心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.54,0:06:01.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,雖然那兩個人今天沒在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.50,0:06:04.43,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但是我可以包辦100人的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.43,0:06:07.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,原來如此 那可太讓人放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.54,0:06:10.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,堪比派張遼守合肥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.74,0:06:14.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你們幹什麼呢 要開門營業囉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.19,0:06:19.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,謝謝大家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.75,0:06:22.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,AZALEA AZALEA…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.24,0:06:25.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,明天幾點入場來著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.13,0:06:29.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,開始記不住日程了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.36,0:06:31.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,粉絲也多起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.87,0:06:34.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,搞不好真有希望在體育場開演唱會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.47,0:06:36.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.12,0:06:43.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.58,0:06:45.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我是帥筍乾DJ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.64,0:06:51.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,而你是在帥筍乾DJ的碟子上起舞的歌姬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.86,0:06:54.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要是不盡全力跟上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.63,0:06:55.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可是會被甩下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.39,0:06:57.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你的意思是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.52,0:06:59.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.55,0:07:02.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我會完成那首歌的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.39,0:07:03.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,太好了 布丁老…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.36,0:07:06.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Kid 那就麻煩您了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.88,0:07:08.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,完成了我會聯繫你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.76,0:07:09.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.05,0:07:10.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.92,0:07:15.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,曲名就叫「六本木烏龍麵店」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.12,0:07:24.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,曲名怎麼取啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.24,0:07:31.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,七海 我贏了布丁老頭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.83,0:07:46.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我非常喜歡在街頭唱歌的七海
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.56,0:07:50.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,七海 你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.12,0:07:53.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒事 只是覺得有點刺眼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.76,0:08:07.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（距離X日還剩5天）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.39,0:08:11.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,話說曲名要怎麼定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.61,0:08:13.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,問我也沒用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:16.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就是想不到特別來電的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.11,0:08:17.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要不就等著靈感降臨唄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.52,0:08:20.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可沒剩多少時間了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.76,0:08:22.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,-對決就在明天\N-哪天投稿來著 10萬讚企劃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.80,0:08:25.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,-想戰勝現在的赤兔馬\N-哪天投稿來著 10萬讚企劃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.07,0:08:26.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,-必須玩命準備才行\N-我想想…5天後
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.35,0:08:29.93,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,完了 我都還沒改編好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.93,0:08:31.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,總之 加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.31,0:08:33.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,別說得這麼輕巧啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.78,0:08:39.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,總之 加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.69,0:08:42.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.78,0:08:44.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,100萬日元
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.24,0:08:45.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,上面寫得很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.80,0:08:46.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（快閃演唱會&贈送100萬日元企劃）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.30,0:08:50.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這下AZALEA就必然能參加SUMMER SONIA了\N（快閃演唱會&贈送100萬日元企劃）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.20,0:08:50.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（快閃演唱會&贈送100萬日元企劃）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.69,0:08:52.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,計劃將在5天後實施\N（快閃演唱會&贈送100萬日元企劃）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.09,0:08:52.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（快閃演唱會&贈送100萬日元企劃）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.45,0:08:54.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你們要在澀谷舉行快閃演唱會\N（快閃演唱會&贈送100萬日元企劃）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.34,0:08:54.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（快閃演唱會&贈送100萬日元企劃）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.82,0:08:55.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我從沒聽說過這事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.24,0:08:57.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我這不是說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.40,0:09:00.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那個 這事太突然了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.16,0:09:02.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,SUMMER SONIA只是前進路上的一站而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.03,0:09:05.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但要是連這次機會都把握不住
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.00,0:09:07.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那想在體育場開演唱會就是痴人說夢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.59,0:09:11.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只要按照我的計劃 就一定能贏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:14.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你們專心表演就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.20,0:09:16.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,無論表演得再好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.37,0:09:20.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,靠錢換讚就沒意義了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.35,0:09:22.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,玩音樂想火就得這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.53,0:09:26.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你們想變回默默無聞的樂隊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.80,0:09:29.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.05,0:09:31.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,英子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.01,0:09:37.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我無法只靠音樂的力量戰鬥了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.11,0:09:40.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,快了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.55,0:09:41.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.74,0:09:43.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,他做足了準備哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.28,0:09:46.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好想在現場看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.64,0:09:49.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你改編完馬上就得錄音吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.62,0:09:51.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.35,0:09:53.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Kid那邊還沒消息嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.80,0:09:56.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,他不是那種會食言的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.58,0:09:58.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我認為只需等待即可
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.01,0:10:00.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,等的時候是最著急的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.75,0:10:03.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,現在就為KABE加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.55,0:10:04.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.60,0:10:08.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,他也是一個為蒼生而戰的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.16,0:10:10.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,停下來 停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.92,0:10:12.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,別發抖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.91,0:10:14.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我是誰 說來聽聽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.16,0:10:16.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.25,0:10:17.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,對 我很清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.87,0:10:19.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我是誰 我是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.33,0:10:21.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,快回想起來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.58,0:10:22.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我是KABE太人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.29,0:10:25.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,說唱對決三連冠的超人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.26,0:10:28.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是在灰燼中重生的不死鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.87,0:10:38.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這是什麼表情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.85,0:10:41.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我真是個徹頭徹尾的膽小普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.47,0:10:43.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.02,0:10:49.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我要為他們代言
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.64,0:10:52.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我要為他們代言
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.77,0:10:54.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我要為他們代言
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.10,0:10:57.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我要為他們和我這樣的人代言
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.96,0:10:59.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,打架最弱也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.64,0:11:01.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只要登上舞台就是最強的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.60,0:11:10.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,最強的赤兔馬功夫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.51,0:11:12.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,敗在這個人手上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.37,0:11:15.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,說唱對決三連冠的說唱機關槍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.39,0:11:16.88,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,回到了舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.20,0:11:19.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,KABE太人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.97,0:11:24.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.59,0:11:26.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.75,0:11:30.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,下面是今天的重頭戲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.05,0:11:31.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,究竟是赤兔馬成功復仇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.75,0:11:34.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還是KABE太人克服空白期
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.50,0:11:37.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,擊敗赤兔馬呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.08,0:11:38.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,太熱血澎湃了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.58,0:11:41.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不知道他有沒有看出我在發抖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.32,0:11:45.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不過 我這是激動得發抖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.53,0:11:48.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,先攻 赤兔馬功夫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.87,0:11:51.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,後攻 KABE太人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.25,0:11:53.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,預備 開始
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.83,0:11:57.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（派對咖孔明）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.87,0:12:00.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,毫不留情 摧毀Pride
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.47,0:12:03.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,將你擊潰赤兔馬Style
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.08,0:12:04.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Yeah 赤兔馬猛烈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.97,0:12:08.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但戰勝他的KABE太人更加Super Big Scale
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.75,0:12:12.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,輸給我竟然耿耿於懷 大失所望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.13,0:12:13.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,話說你 虛張聲勢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.87,0:12:16.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你或許當這是雪恥戰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.21,0:12:18.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不管比幾次 我都能輕鬆獲勝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.82,0:12:20.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,今天你也必將鎩羽而歸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.87,0:12:21.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,學到了沒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.85,0:12:24.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,吸取教訓再來對擂 Hey Yo
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.12,0:12:26.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你逃避對決逃避我 幾多惆悵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.62,0:12:29.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我窮追猛打 讓你無處藏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.22,0:12:31.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我要用真正的實力 掃蕩掃蕩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.50,0:12:34.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,銘刻在你全身 永不遺忘
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.30,0:12:36.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,讓你見識 全新景致
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.87,0:12:39.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,一路累積起的歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.38,0:12:41.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你要是怕得發抖 那就借你我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.72,0:12:44.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我的背影 你看好別走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.09,0:12:47.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,果然好強
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.46,0:12:49.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,KABE看起來好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.94,0:12:50.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.24,0:12:54.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,咦？節奏這麼慢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.09,0:12:56.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,感覺好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.77,0:12:58.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.71,0:13:02.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,該說什麼 我早就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.32,0:13:04.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.90,0:13:07.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你的位置 不在我路途
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.46,0:13:10.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我要走我自己的道路 For My Life
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.09,0:13:11.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,而且我並不孤單
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.36,0:13:13.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,與同伴並肩前行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.00,0:13:15.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,向著終點 Action
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.16,0:13:17.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我懷疑過自己的說唱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.74,0:13:20.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,越是懷疑 越要將懦弱Knock Out
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.29,0:13:23.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我要堅持自我 將你拿下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.27,0:13:25.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,然後站上頂點 君臨天下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.65,0:13:27.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,結束
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.75,0:13:36.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那麼 接下來進行評判
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.77,0:13:39.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我將舉起勝者的手…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.77,0:13:56.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是你贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.19,0:13:59.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,承讓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.54,0:14:04.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,勝者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.14,0:14:07.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,KABE太人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.37,0:14:25.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.82,0:14:27.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,KABE太厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.54,0:14:30.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,看來他不再是吳下阿蒙了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.38,0:14:31.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.89,0:14:33.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是指呂蒙對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.71,0:14:34.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,呂什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.63,0:14:36.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,吳國武將呂蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.72,0:14:38.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,最初學識不怎麼行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.25,0:14:40.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但是經過刻苦學習
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.44,0:14:43.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,他的智謀超過了普通的軍師
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.04,0:14:45.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,讓大家大吃一驚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.10,0:14:48.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真的呢 KABE的說唱比之前更有…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.46,0:14:49.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那個詞是什麼來著
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.77,0:14:51.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,感染力對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.70,0:14:54.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,對 感染力高了好多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.47,0:14:57.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,士別三日當刮目相待
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.91,0:14:59.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,堅持努力的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.51,0:15:02.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,哪怕只是三天沒見 都有顯著的進步
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.73,0:15:03.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（Kid：完成了）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.13,0:15:04.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（Kid：完成了）\N就是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.61,0:15:05.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（Kid：完成了）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.32,0:15:08.88,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,接下來輪到你了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.51,0:15:10.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.75,0:15:18.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我也可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.77,0:15:22.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,下次再見面時 要讓她大吃一驚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.05,0:15:26.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我能成為這樣的歌手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.16,0:15:29.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.27,0:15:31.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.02,0:15:35.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我要成為這樣的歌手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.38,0:15:38.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.08,0:15:40.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.60,0:15:44.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,看來你已經準備好在我的碟子上起舞了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.89,0:15:46.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那就趕緊開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.90,0:15:47.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.87,0:15:53.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,現在問可能已經晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.07,0:15:56.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,現在才錄音真的來得及嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.47,0:16:00.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,看過便知
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.87,0:16:03.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,英子 我要放歌囉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.09,0:16:05.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要是準備好了就從第二遍開始唱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.61,0:16:06.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.58,0:16:23.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不愧是走向世界的Steve Kid
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.05,0:16:25.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真不是浪得虛名
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.39,0:16:34.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好厲害 這真的是我寫的歌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.25,0:16:37.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好想唱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.07,0:16:39.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好想立刻唱唱看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.17,0:16:43.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,賭局是我輸了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.35,0:16:47.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,哦？可你怎麼看起來如此開心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.26,0:16:50.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,能幹份好活 心情自然好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.40,0:16:53.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但是我特別討厭輸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.75,0:16:55.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那麼下次跟人決勝時
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.07,0:16:59.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,最好是把對方拉到自己的戰場上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.50,0:17:03.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,致人而不致於人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.92,0:17:06.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,當我提出要跟你賭一把時
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.01,0:17:10.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你就已經對英子抱有不少期待了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.08,0:17:13.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,讓對方決定賭什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.61,0:17:17.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,等於是主動進入對方擅長的戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.75,0:17:21.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只要你聽了英子的歌 就一定會接受這工作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.50,0:17:25.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我對此深信不疑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.59,0:17:29.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,馬後炮誰不會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.73,0:17:32.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,英子 那我要開始放第二遍了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.72,0:17:44.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我覺得是時候放棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.38,0:17:45.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我要成為你的軍師
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.29,0:17:46.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,唱那首吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.07,0:17:47.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,唱給更多人聽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.35,0:17:48.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你缺乏自我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.11,0:17:49.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要一起唱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.52,0:17:51.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我要唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.95,0:17:54.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我要傾盡一切
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.49,0:18:03.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,老師 孔明老師
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.13,0:18:10.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,老師 現在可不是悠哉睡午覺的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.22,0:18:15.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.06,0:18:18.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我回來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.14,0:18:20.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,劉皇叔在門口等你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.98,0:18:22.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這是他第三次來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.11,0:18:26.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,-劉皇叔 -他說見不到你就不走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.66,0:18:27.88,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我的主公？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.56,0:18:30.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.79,0:18:34.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我這是置身於往昔的記憶中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.08,0:18:38.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,大夢誰先覺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.96,0:18:41.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,平生我自知
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.79,0:18:44.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,草堂春睡足
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.68,0:18:47.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,窗外日遲遲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.42,0:18:48.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.80,0:18:51.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,去告訴劉皇叔 我馬上就過去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.92,0:19:12.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我的主公
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.80,0:19:17.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好生愜意的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.75,0:19:18.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,孔明老師
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.57,0:19:20.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,終於見到您了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.18,0:19:23.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,讓您見笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.86,0:19:26.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這是我兒時學的兒歌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.14,0:19:38.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我的憂國憂民之心與您一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.02,0:19:42.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,如不治之症 時刻折磨著我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.28,0:19:45.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,蒼生的哀嘆遍布大地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.29,0:19:47.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我想在天下行大義
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.18,0:19:51.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,創造太平盛世
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.59,0:19:55.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,孔明老師 還請助我一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.25,0:20:03.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我的主公 我諸葛亮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.52,0:20:06.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,定當為您鞠躬盡瘁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.78,0:20:11.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,孔明 孔明
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.83,0:20:15.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,你怎麼了 孔明
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.24,0:20:16.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼呆住了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.73,0:20:17.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.70,0:20:21.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,歌聲實在是太美妙 似乎讓我的意識穿越了時空
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.15,0:20:22.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,太誇張了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.84,0:20:24.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不 你真的好厲害啊 英子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.88,0:20:27.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,經過這一週 感覺你唱得更好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.79,0:20:29.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,總之 你唱得太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.86,0:20:33.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真討厭 用力誇我也沒好處的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.89,0:20:35.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還差得遠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.38,0:20:38.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我還要繼續改到滿意為止
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.61,0:20:41.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,別糟蹋了我的改編哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.71,0:20:42.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.42,0:20:45.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,天下太平的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.14,0:20:48.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,帶我走上無盡旅途的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.56,0:20:50.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,-是我的主公\N-可是 你是怎麼練得這麼好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.90,0:20:52.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,-就是你吧\N-可是 你是怎麼練得這麼好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.75,0:20:55.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,哪有 我沒做什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.99,0:21:00.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,反反覆覆的Every day
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.60,0:21:04.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,連哭泣都忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.41,0:21:07.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,將失去色彩的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.20,0:21:07.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,抱在懷裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.75,0:21:11.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,（距離X日還剩3天）\N抱在懷裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.84,0:21:15.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,即使遍體鱗傷 It's all right
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.58,0:21:18.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,將傷痕當成勳章
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.59,0:21:19.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Live your life
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.96,0:21:23.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,So you want to be free
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.91,0:21:26.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可以聽見嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.51,0:21:33.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,勇敢面對逆風吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.90,0:21:37.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,風強正合我意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.98,0:21:40.93,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Change the world
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.93,0:21:43.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.10,0:22:13.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(夢想家)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.06,0:22:15.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Hey DJ 躁起來 yeah yeah yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.99,0:22:17.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,來段心情上好↑↑的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.96,0:22:21.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,針丟地上 音樂響起 派對之夜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.77,0:22:25.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,喝吧 來 來 來 大家一起跳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.63,0:22:27.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Hip-Pop People
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.11,0:22:32.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,撥打那奇蹟Number
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.67,0:22:39.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Yo！在這時代分享的MUSIC
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.01,0:22:41.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,想將其找出 轉動地球儀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.00,0:22:44.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,生活動盪不穩 所以要重視平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.79,0:22:47.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,生活並非全是好事 所以「還能拼！」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.16,0:22:48.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,踢開糟糕的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.68,0:22:50.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,按下重啟的按鈕！
